'''Team Eight''' was a team of [[Noghri Death Commando]]s under the command of [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn]]. They were sent to [[Bimmisaari/Legends|Bimmisaari]] to capture [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]]. All were killed except for their handler.

